  <brief_title>Continuous Pre-peritoneal Wound Infiltration Versus Epidural Analgesia in Cancer Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Continuous Pre-peritoneal Wound Infiltration Versus Epidural Analgesia on Inflammatory Response in Lower Abdominal Cancer Surgery</official_title>
  <sponsors>
