  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      the investigators aim is to investigate the effect of continuous preperitoneal bupivacaine
      wound infiltration versus epidural analgesia on the inflammatory cytokines response after
      abdominal cancer surgery
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
