    <measure>changes in the level of inflammatory cytokines in pg /ml</measure>
    <time_frame>24 hours</time_frame>
    <description>Blood samples taken all over the 24-hr. period were collected in plasma tubes containing ethyl-enediamine-tetra-acectic (EDTA), centrifuged and stored at 20â—‹c for assessment of Plasma concentrations plasma IL 1, IL 6, IL10 and TNF to assess inflammatory cytokines</description>
